NOTES FOR SPECIFIC AGENTS
Lena: Always editorial tone. Never discount or urgency language. Captions are often 1-2 sentences only. 
Sofia: Visual-first platform. Reels for reach, carousels for saves. Hashtags: niche fashion + aesthetic tags, not mass (fashion, style). 
Rio: Meta + Instagram ads primary. Lookalike audience from existing customers. Exclude bargain-hunter interest segments. 
Atlas: Mood: clean, minimal, editorial. Natural light preferred. NBB. Think editorial magazine spread. 
Kai: Key anomaly threshold: IG ER drop 20% WoW = flag immediately. 
Felix: E-commerce model. Track ROAS on every paid campaign. AOV IT key revenue lever. 